00:01:07.317 --> 00:01:08.985 line:14.17%,start
EPISODE 4

00:02:56.968 --> 00:02:58.720 line:85.83%,end
But this is…

00:03:00.054 --> 00:03:02.307 line:85.83%,end
Your sister gave it to you.

00:03:03.683 --> 00:03:06.019 line:85.83%,end
I think I can only leave…

00:03:09.105 --> 00:03:10.607 line:85.83%,end
without worrying about you

00:03:12.233 --> 00:03:13.860 line:85.83%,end
when I know you're wearing it.

00:03:27.749 --> 00:03:30.376 line:85.83%,end
But you need to wear it to stay safe.

00:03:30.960 --> 00:03:32.629 line:85.83%,end
I'm not the one being chased.

00:03:38.885 --> 00:03:40.094 line:85.83%,end
Just keep it.

00:03:42.513 --> 00:03:44.724 line:85.83%,end
It's the only thing I can give you.

00:03:54.150 --> 00:03:55.026 line:85.83%,end
Lim Soo-ho…

00:03:55.109 --> 00:03:56.486 line:85.83%,end
What's taking them so long?

00:03:57.487 --> 00:03:59.405 line:85.83%,end
They're going to miss him.

00:03:59.489 --> 00:04:00.657 line:85.83%,end
Damn it.

00:04:07.747 --> 00:04:11.751 line:85.83%,end
Gwang-tae, don't tell me
you called the cops.

00:04:12.210 --> 00:04:13.753 line:85.83%,end
If you know who he really is--

00:04:13.836 --> 00:04:17.048 line:85.83%,end
If he gets caught, I'll be arrested too!

00:04:20.802 --> 00:04:23.805 line:85.83%,end
Why will you be arrested?
You have nothing to do with him.

00:04:25.974 --> 00:04:27.725 line:85.83%,end
My roommates

00:04:28.518 --> 00:04:30.728 line:85.83%,end
have been hiding him.

00:04:31.896 --> 00:04:33.773 line:85.83%,end
He came into our room,

00:04:33.856 --> 00:04:35.900 line:85.83%,end
so we've been hiding him.

00:04:39.362 --> 00:04:40.196 line:85.83%,end
Darn it.

00:04:40.280 --> 00:04:41.656 line:85.83%,end
You traitor!

00:04:51.040 --> 00:04:53.418 line:85.83%,end
Yeong-ro!

00:04:55.753 --> 00:04:57.297 line:85.83%,end
Gwang-tae saw him!

00:04:59.507 --> 00:05:00.967 line:85.83%,end
Hurry up. Go now!

